Festival of Dangerous Ideas,

00:00:07.310 --> 00:00:09.009
We are the Gods, Now.

00:00:09.009 --> 00:00:10.800
I'm Ann Mossop from
the Sydney Opera House.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:13.440
I'm one of the curators of the
Festival of Dangerous Ideas,

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:15.940
